data.name: AWS Roche Decrypt
data.xml_template:
<route id="{{source}}" group="">
    <from uri="direct:{{source}}"/>
    <setHeader name="cacheCapacity">
        <constant>{{cache.cacheCapacity}}</constant>
    </setHeader>
    <setHeader name="maxEntryAge">
        <constant>{{cache.maxEntryAge}}</constant>
    </setHeader>
    <setHeader name="maxEntryMsg">
        <constant>{{cache.maxEntryMsg}}</constant>
    </setHeader>
    <setHeader name="byteUseLimit">
        <constant>{{cache.byteUseLimit}}</constant>
    </setHeader>

    <setHeader name="partition">
        <constant>{{aws-key-config.partition}}</constant>
    </setHeader>
    <setHeader name="accountIds">
        <constant>{{aws-key-config.accountIds}}</constant>
    </setHeader>
    <setHeader name="keyAlias">
        <constant>{{aws-key-config.keyAlias}}</constant>
    </setHeader>
    <setHeader name="region">
        <constant>{{aws-key-config.region}}</constant>
    </setHeader>
    <setHeader name="proxyUrl">
        <constant>{{aws-key-config.proxyUrl}}</constant>
    </setHeader>

    <setHeader name="commitmentPolicy">
        <constant>{{policies.commitmentPolicy}}</constant>
    </setHeader>
    <setHeader name="encryptionAlgorithm">
        <constant>{{policies.encryptionAlgorithm}}</constant>
    </setHeader>
    <setHeader name="secretKeyType">
        <constant>{{policies.secretKeyType}}</constant>
    </setHeader>
    <setHeader name="secretKeyLength">
        <constant>{{policies.secretKeyLength}}</constant>
    </setHeader>
    <setHeader name="keyId">
        <constant>{{policies.keyId}}</constant>
    </setHeader>
    <setHeader name="providerName">
        <constant>{{policies.providerName}}</constant>
    </setHeader>

    <process ref="decryptEventProcessor"/>
    {{generateDestination target}}
</route>
